ies. The oscillations at high\nand low frequencies are more pronounced in different parts of the loop\n(depending on the loop orientation). The layers where the line-of-sight\ncomponent of the magnetic field changes sign can produce additional\npeculiarities in the oscillation patterns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Feb 2015 08:55:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
